OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSunny spells and occasional
OL,6,Fshowers through the day, some of which
OL,7,Fcould be heavy and thundery during the
OL,8,Fafternoon. Winds are light but breezy
OL,9,Falong the coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FShowers easing during the
OL,12,Fevening, then clouding over from the
OL,13,Fwest with rain arriving during the
OL,14,Fearly hours. Feeling cold in the
OL,15,Fincreasingly breezy wind.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FCloudy and breezy, with early
OL,18,Frain slowly clearing to the east
OL,19,Ffollowed by frequent heavy showers in
OL,20,Fthe afternoon and well into the
OL,21,Fevening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
