OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FWednesday breezy with showers.
OL,7,FBecoming more settled on Thursday with
OL,8,Fonly the odd isolated shower. A dry
OL,9,Fand warm day on Friday with coastal
OL,10,Fshowers. Temperatures near average,
OL,11,Ftrending upwards.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
